===家庭===
1955年，希尔和贝蒂结婚。因为希尔将他所有的财产都用于了他的赛车事业上，贝蒂支付了婚礼的费用。希尔以后两个女儿——布丽奇特（Brigitte）、萨曼莎（Samantha）和一个儿子——[[达蒙·希尔|达蒙·希尔]]。达蒙·希尔获得1996年[[F1|F1]][[F1世界车手冠军列表|车手世界冠军]]。

===逝世===
{{quote box|quote=IN MEMORY OF GRAHAM HILL. TWICE WORLD CHAMPION RACING DRIVER WHO DIED WITH FIVE COLLEAGUES WHEN THEIR AIRCRAFT CRASHED HERE IN FREEZING FOG 29TH NOVEMBER 1975|source=位于阿克莱高尔夫球场的纪念碑上的文字|width=25%|align=left}}

1975年11月，希尔从法国保罗·里卡多赛道返回英国.但是飞机试图在大雾情况下降落[[埃爾斯特里飛行場|埃爾斯特里飛行場]]时发生意外，最终在[[伦敦|伦敦]]北部的阿克莱高尔夫球场附近坠毁。<ref name=Hillreg>{{cite web |url=http://www.aaib.gov.uk/cms_resources.cfm?file=/14-1976%20N6645Y.pdf |title=Aircraft Accident Report 14/76 |publisher=Accidents Investigation Board |date=29 September 1976 |accessdate=25 November 2011 |archive-date=2014-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140518015529/http://www.aaib.gov.uk/cms_resources.cfm?file=%2F14-1976%20N6645Y.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref> 这次失事还导致{{link-en|希尔车队|Embassy Hill}}经理雷·布林布尔，技师托尼·阿尔科克和泰瑞·理查德，车手{{link-en|托尼·布赖斯|Tony Brise}}和设计师安迪·斯摩曼五人死亡。<ref>{{cite news|title=Racing Mourns Death of Graham Hill|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ioVQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2BEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7248,127474&dq=graham+hill&hl=en|newspaper=The Milwaukee Sentinel|date=1 December 1975|page=5|accessdate=2014-03-09|archive-date=2015-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017154408/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ioVQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2BEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7248,127474&dq=graham+hill&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

希尔的葬礼在[[圣奥尔本斯座堂|圣奥尔本斯座堂]]举行，他被埋葬在了St Botolphs Church。

在希尔死后，银石赛道所在地银石镇决定以希尔之名命名一条道路。<ref name="GrahamHillLocation">[http://maps.google.co.uk/maps?f=q&hl=en&q=graham+hill,+silverstone&safe=on&ie=UTF8&t=h&om=1 Graham Hill] {{Wayback|url=http://maps.google.co.uk/maps?f=q&hl=en&q=graham+hill,+silverstone&safe=on&ie=UTF8&t=h&om=1 |date=20110607153047 }}, [[Google_Maps|Google Maps]]</ref>布兰兹-哈奇赛道的“格雷厄姆·希尔弯”也是为了纪念希尔而以他的名字命名的。一块[[蓝色牌匾|蓝色牌匾]]也刻在了希尔在伦敦的住处来纪念他。<ref name='EngHet'>{{cite web| url=http://www.english-heritage.org.uk/discover/blue-plaques/search/hill-graham-1929-1975| title=HILL, GRAHAM (1929-1975)| publisher=English Heritage| accessdate=2012-08-04| archive-date=2014-03-11| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311164626/http://www.english-heritage.org.uk/discover/blue-plaques/search/hill-graham-1929-1975| dead-url=no}}</ref>

